Package: Healthmetrics
Title: Health Metrics Calculation and Classification Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Obehi", "Ikpea", , "oikpea@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The Healthmetrics package provides functions for calculating 
    and classifying various health metrics such as blood pressure categories, 
    cholesterol levels, and Body Mass Index (BMI). It offers easy-to-use 
    functions that prompt the user for necessary inputs and output the 
    respective health classifications based on standard medical guidelines.
